window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Look out! Karma is behind the wheel of the bus, headed straight through town.</p> <p>When a senator’s niece is found dead in Stonebridge, the whole town gets tipped on its head. Many think she got what she deserved, but Peter must still bring the killer to justice. Hazel wants to help, but with the feds involved, Peter has to push her away.</p> <p>It’s not Hazel’s fault that people confide in her, but keeping their secrets will strain her relationship with Peter...and the law. She’ll have to put on her striped stockings and learn some scary new spells in order to get out of this one.</p> <p><i>Three Times Charmed</i> is the third audiobook in the Teas and Temptations Cozy Mystery series. If you like lighthearted paranormal mysteries with a fun romance, then you’ll love Cindy Stark’s magical adventures!</p>"; 
